title: 'Good steady Hardcase Trolley bag'

title: 'Defective lock'
body: Safari is a reputed brand and I bought it with great hope. It's too light but for my first trip to US I had no problem ,since it was opened and locked just four times. This month I made another trip in which I was staying at many hotels and had to open and lock multiple times.The second day itself the number lock could not be opened and it had to be forced open.For the rest of the trip we had to buy an additional TSA lock. This month I had bought a cabin baggage for the same trip and that too had the same problem.Since warranty is there I hope to get a refund.But the inconvenience caused was so much we will think twice before buying again
